                                                "body": "Buildings <span class=\"code_addition\">are to</span> be designed and constructed in accordance with the <span class=\"code_addition\">applicable provisions of the \"</span>International Energy Conservation Code<span class=\"code_addition\">\" or the requirements of \"ASHRAE 90.1\" listed in Chapter 35 of this code except\nas modified in Sections 1301.2 and 1301.3. </span>",
