                                            "13",
                                            "1301"
                                        ],
                                        "body": "The following changes are made to the International Energy Conservation Code:<br/><br/>\n<div><b>Residential Provisions</b></div>\n<ol>\n<li><b>Section R403.3.7 is to read: \"Building cavities (Mandatory).</b> Building framing cavities are not to be used as supply ducts.\"</li>\n</ol>\n<div><b>Commercial Provisions</b></div>\n<ol>\n<li>Add a new paragraph at the end of <b>Section C402.1 General </b>that reads: \"Compliance with ACI/TMS 122.1 is permitted for mitigating the effects of thermal bridges in <a class=\"autolink\" href=\"/viewer/ohio/ibc-2021/chapter/2/definitions#duped_concrete_\">concrete</a> or <a class=\"autolink\" href=\"/viewer/ohio/ibc-2021/chapter/2/definitions#masonry_\">masonry</a> assemblies.\"</li>\n<li><b>Section C405.11 <a class=\"autolink\" href=\"/viewer/ohio/ibc-2021/chapter/2/definitions#automatic_\">Automatic</a> Receptacle Control:</b> Delete section and subsections.</li>\n<li><b>Section C405.12 Energy Monitoring:</b> Delete section and subsections.</li>\n<li><b><a class=\"autolink\" href=\"/viewer/ohio/ibc-2021/chapter/6/types-of-construction#6\">Chapter 6</a> Referenced Standards:</b> Add promulgating agencies American <a class=\"autolink\" href=\"/viewer/ohio/ibc-2021/chapter/2/definitions#duped_concrete_\">Concrete</a> Institute (ACI), 38800 Country Club Drive, Farmington Hills, MI 48331 and The <a class=\"autolink\" href=\"/viewer/ohio/ibc-2021/chapter/2/definitions#masonry_\">Masonry</a> Society (TMS), 105 South Sunset Street, Suite Q, Longmont, CO 80501 and Referenced standard ACI-TMS Code 122.1-21 titled <i>Thermal Bridge Mitigation for Buildings having <a class=\"autolink\" href=\"/viewer/ohio/ibc-2021/chapter/2/definitions#duped_concrete_\">Concrete</a> and <a class=\"autolink\" href=\"/viewer/ohio/ibc-2021/chapter/2/definitions#masonry_\">Masonry</a> <a class=\"autolink\" href=\"/viewer/ohio/ibc-2021/chapter/2/definitions#wall_\">Walls</a> and <a class=\"autolink\" href=\"/viewer/ohio/ibc-2021/chapter/2/definitions#masonry_\">Masonry</a> <a class=\"autolink\" href=\"/viewer/ohio/ibc-2021/chapter/2/definitions#veneer_\">Veneer</a>- Code Requirements and Commentary.</i></li>\n</ol>",
                                        "depth": 2,
                                        "diagrams": [],
                                        "displayRef": "1301.2",
                                        "displayTitle": "1301.2 Modifications to the International Energy Conservation Code",
                                        "hasAssemblies": false,
                                        "isContiguous": true,
                                        "numAssembliesOnRef": 0,
                                        "numBuildingProductsOnRef": 0,
                                        "numDiagramsOnRef": 0,
